      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small dents on the body panels. The interior shows visible wear on the seats and carpeting consistent with regular use. It is currently operational and runs as expected.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
