    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it is solid and drives reliably, with all major systems functioning as they should. The interior is clean and comfortable, though you will find some minor signs of use on the upholstery and trim. The exterior paint still holds a nice shine, but there are a few small stone chips and light surface scratches expected for its age. Overall, it\u2019s a dependable and presentable car that is ready for its next owner with no major repairs needed.",
      "price": 33750.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
