      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera represents the pinnacle of the analog driving experience, featuring the refined 3.6L flat-six engine equipped with VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transaxle, delivering power through a perfectly balanced chassis. This example is mechanically superlative; the IMS bearing has been proactively upgraded to a ceramic solution, and the rear main seal remains bone dry. The suspension geometry is factory-perfect, providing telepathic feedback through the hydraulic steering rack. With zero evidence of bore scoring and a flawless DME overrev report, this collector-grade vehicle offers impeccable performance and aesthetic purity.",
